data.title: WMYJ (AM)
data.meta_description: WMYJ is a radio station licensed to Martinsville, Indiana, United States. The station is owned by Mid-America Radio Group and broadcasts an Adult contemporary format.
data.text:
WMYJ (1540 AM) is a radio station licensed to Martinsville, Indiana, United States. The station is owned by Mid-America Radio Group[2][3] and broadcasts an Adult contemporary format.
